### QR Code vCard API Test File
### Update the @baseUrl to match your local development port

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7163

### Generate QR Code as PNG Image (Download)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vcardqr/generate?format=image
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-0123",
  "organization": "Acme Corporation",
  "title": "Software Engineer",
  "street": "123 Main Street",
  "city": "New York",
  "state": "NY",
  "postalCode": "10001",
  "country": "USA",
  "website": "https://johndoe.com",
  "notes": "Available for consulting"
}

###

### Generate QR Code as PDF (Download)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vcardqr/generate?format=pdf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-0456",
  "organization": "Tech Innovations Inc",
  "title": "Product Manager",
  "street": "456 Oak Avenue",
  "city": "San Francisco",
  "state": "CA",
  "postalCode": "94102",
  "country": "USA",
  "website": "https://janesmith.dev"
}

###

### Generate QR Code as PNG (Download)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vcardqr/generate?format=png
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Michael",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "m.johnson@company.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-0789"
}

###

### Generate QR Code - Return Base64 Image in JSON (Best for Web Display)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vcardqr/generate?format=both
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Williams",
  "email": "alice.williams@tech.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-0999",
  "organization": "Digital Solutions LLC",
  "title": "Design Lead"
}

###

### Generate QR Code - Minimal Request (Only First Name Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vcardqr/generate?format=image
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Sarah"
}

###

### Test Error Handling - Missing Required Field (FirstName)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vcardqr/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lastName": "Test",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

